Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.28,0:00:06.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界因ZERO创造的奇迹而改变
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.23,0:00:11.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界因ZERO所展现的行动而重生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.37,0:00:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 当今世界正迈向新纪元
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.00,0:00:22.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伴随着无数欲望与情感的波浪 ZERO必须前进
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.95,0:00:25.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是为了让时针继续前行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.50,0:00:31.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和约定的一样 我一个人来了 到底怎么回事 杰雷米亚君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.98,0:00:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说皇女殿下的消息只能告诉我一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.23,0:02:11.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,土之味
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.42,0:02:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑骑士团正朝着鹿儿岛沿岸前进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.45,0:02:26.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是请大家放心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:30.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我布里塔尼亚在Knight of One瓦尔德施泰因卿的指挥下…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.01,0:02:35.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里已是布里塔尼亚的领土
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.20,0:02:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一兵一卒都别让他登陆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.59,0:02:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人中计了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.54,0:02:44.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天英方向应该会薄弱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.70,0:02:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让登陆部队咬上去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:48.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌军朝着山口进发
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.26,0:02:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加西亚队全灭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.70,0:02:52.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑骑士团这些家伙 竟投入了这么多战力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.62,0:02:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算想维持国土绝对防卫线 东中华海战却一直被星刻压着打
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.37,0:02:59.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要惊慌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.97,0:03:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要守住11区 以奥德修斯殿下为首的皇族都将入侵超合众国
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.60,0:03:11.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其余的Knight of Rounds也将全体奔赴前线
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.07,0:03:19.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是只要解放日本的话 布里塔尼亚的殖民地将一个个奋起反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.21,0:03:22.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界地图将重新绘制
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.96,0:03:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是天王山
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.04,0:03:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经过去八年了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.68,0:03:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和娜娜莉被托付给这枢木神社
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.91,0:03:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.92,0:03:42.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 布里塔尼亚小子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.67,0:03:44.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.73,0:03:46.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次遇见了朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:50.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我救我想救的人 不需要什么理由
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.14,0:03:53.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久以前就是个不懂得变通的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.23,0:03:58.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是正因为如此 你成了我生平第一个朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.85,0:04:05.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 朱雀 我想赌在你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假如你能够接受我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.41,0:04:21.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不够打啊 这种程度的祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.27,0:04:24.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亚的吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.01,0:04:25.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:26.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六角突贯阵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.49,0:04:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提问
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:40.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最珍贵的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.00,0:04:42.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.26,0:04:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 是生命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:45.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.63,0:04:51.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星刻大人 左翼崩坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.47,0:04:54.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一架突破能力超强的Knightmare
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:56.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让英迪拉队去援护
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:05:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左翼全体保持后退 把那台机体孤立起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.60,0:05:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.83,0:05:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修奈泽尔皇子应该还留在东京
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.52,0:05:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么可担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:10.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九州那边有帝国最强骑士Knight of One在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.23,0:05:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就留在东京 给他国一种“这只不过是场小纷争”的印象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.09,0:05:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes Your Highness
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.90,0:05:24.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.99,0:05:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场战斗很快就会结束
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.41,0:05:29.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假如我没有判断错的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.59,0:05:33.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在长崎出现的伏兵 被Grausam Valkyrie队消灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.76,0:05:35.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向岛根派遣增援部队
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.76,0:05:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正面 也让莫利卿去援护
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.63,0:05:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡利姆卿后撤 和拉斯科卿汇合重新编队
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.61,0:05:42.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人的攻势看来快停了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.02,0:05:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦尔德施泰因大人出击的话 一口气解决他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.29,0:05:47.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.34,0:05:53.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太弱了 以ZERO的作战而言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.91,0:05:55.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Galahad出发
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.62,0:05:57.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一特装使用援护装备
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.01,0:05:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Galahad出发!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.15,0:06:04.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.85,0:06:06.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你说好了的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.78,0:06:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亏你能来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:11.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亚在特殊情况下 会设置31种路线
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.48,0:06:15.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中对关系到皇族的线路尤其松懈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.90,0:06:17.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你错了 鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:21.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,‘亏你敢在我面前出现’
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:23.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是这意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.55,0:06:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是约定?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今谁还会相信你的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.54,0:06:32.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你为什么也一个人来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.90,0:06:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.11,0:06:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我不想再撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.22,0:06:41.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像对娜娜莉撒谎的你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.01,0:06:44.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最差劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.44,0:06:46.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.37,0:06:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明一直背叛着我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.50,0:06:50.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.85,0:06:55.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对学生会的同伴 对娜娜莉也是 就连尤菲…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.07,0:06:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样好吗 藤堂先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.80,0:07:01.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.07,0:07:03.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO的联络还没有来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.29,0:07:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是Knight of Rounds都出现了 就算是星刻总司令也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.39,0:07:09.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.66,0:07:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能够相信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:14.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擅自跟Orange、罗洛之流同伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.46,0:07:16.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不觉得秘密太多了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.86,0:07:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这之前也秘密派遣木下他们…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.67,0:07:22.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO对目前的我们来说是必须的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:25.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是和扇他们说了很多次了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.59,0:07:27.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 日本解放以后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.91,0:07:29.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.04,0:07:36.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扇和迪特哈尔特去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.99,0:07:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:41.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想威胁我做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.66,0:07:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威胁? 不不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想让你作为黑骑士团的一员 一如既往的工作而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.22,0:07:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.58,0:07:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是希望你不要妨碍ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.59,0:07:56.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 能代替我的人有一大把…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.19,0:07:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为你平凡 所以你的存在才有价值
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,组织这种东西 成员各个都很耀眼是不能维持的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.73,0:08:15.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想确认一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.03,0:08:18.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有没有对尤菲使用GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.12,0:08:20.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.42,0:08:23.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你让她屠杀日本人?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.25,0:08:26.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我下令的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.83,0:08:28.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么下达这种GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:30.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:33.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让日本人奋起反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.18,0:08:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日本行政特区成立的话 黑骑士团就崩溃了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.09,0:08:40.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏莉之死呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.30,0:08:42.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.82,0:08:45.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.41,0:08:51.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你来说 夏莉和尤菲都只不过是实现野心的棋子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.64,0:08:54.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 所有的罪都在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.03,0:08:57.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这和娜娜莉无关
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.42,0:08:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.70,0:09:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搬出娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.91,0:09:03.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.90,0:09:10.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 哥哥为了我 一直扮演着圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.84,0:09:13.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温柔的哥哥的外表和ZERO的面具
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.77,0:09:15.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪个才是真正的鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.79,0:09:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 连这里都没来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:20.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀没来这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.57,0:09:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把洪古的部队投入左翼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.66,0:09:28.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备第二次突击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.07,0:09:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阁下是指挥官吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.08,0:09:35.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擒王来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.79,0:09:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说是战术的基本…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:55.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是Excalibur
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.97,0:09:59.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇帝亲自命名的圣剑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.51,0:10:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我生平第一次向人低头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.26,0:10:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顾不得体面了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.16,0:10:10.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除此以外我别无所求
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.21,0:10:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算GEASS也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.81,0:10:14.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 救救娜娜莉吧 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.96,0:10:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今…你这算啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:21.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为你会被原谅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.17,0:10:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.73,0:10:27.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 现在我只能这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.49,0:10:30.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想救娜娜莉 只有靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:33.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你当我会原谅你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.29,0:10:35.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家会原谅你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.56,0:10:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被你骗的人 因你而死的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:41.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有尤菲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今知道认错的话 就把尤菲给我复活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.57,0:10:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:53.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用你的恶意挽救世界给我看看 现在立刻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.73,0:10:56.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是创造奇迹的ZERO吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.57,0:10:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有什么奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.55,0:11:00.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都是计算和演出的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.56,0:11:02.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,称为ZERO的假面只是记号
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.98,0:11:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是为了撒谎而制造的装置
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.38,0:11:06.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么装置
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:09.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为这种藉口能说得过去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.57,0:11:12.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是谎言的话 就给我圆谎到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:15.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是过去不会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.64,0:11:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有办法重新来过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我 鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.69,0:11:24.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么给我下了“活下去”的GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.80,0:11:26.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.12,0:11:38.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对我下的“活下去”的GEASS 扭曲了我的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:40.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么对我下那样的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.42,0:11:44.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我想活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.28,0:11:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我因涉嫌暗杀克洛维斯殿下而被问罪 你为什么要救我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.25,0:11:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了获取日本人的信任
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酒店劫持事件 营救学生会成员又是为了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.46,0:11:58.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想利用它让黑骑士团亮相
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.81,0:12:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这眼神…我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.35,0:12:08.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是隐藏秘密接受惩罚的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.97,0:12:11.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我加入了布里塔尼亚军
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.30,0:12:15.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了补偿 为了不让悲剧重演
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.12,0:12:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是谎言吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.11,0:12:24.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修 有一个补偿你谎言的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.50,0:12:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是让你的谎言成真
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:31.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你谎称你是正义的伙伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.49,0:12:36.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就成为真正的正义的伙伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.65,0:12:39.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把谎言撒到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.72,0:12:42.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.16,0:12:47.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束这场战争 如果你是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.05,0:12:49.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这是只有ZERO才能做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.67,0:12:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用让世界变得和平 大家变得幸福的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.16,0:12:56.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么做的话 我就把娜娜莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:12:59.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救出来?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了娜娜莉 再一次与你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.25,0:13:07.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.69,0:13:11.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你的话 无论什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.50,0:13:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.16,0:13:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止了 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.62,0:13:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经知道你的真面目了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:21.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧 枢木卿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.89,0:13:22.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.62,0:13:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.79,0:13:26.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你从一开始就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.62,0:13:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.16,0:13:31.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你立下大功了 枢木卿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.72,0:13:33.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样战争就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.68,0:13:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 你又打算出卖我才…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:40.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你背叛我 朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:43.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你背叛了我!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.56,0:13:50.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为最近朱雀的样子有点奇怪 就觉得他是不是有所松懈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.64,0:13:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是在学生会室发现的?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.37,0:13:55.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 当成宝贝似的放在储物柜里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.24,0:13:58.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多地方都被撕掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.17,0:14:04.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你… 和恐怖份子关系融洽的情形也许不太好留下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.92,0:14:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 大家一起么就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.29,0:14:10.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是么 那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.48,0:14:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也会流露出这样的表情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.81,0:14:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从没见过朱雀像这样的笑过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:19.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.34,0:14:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.27,0:14:23.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是布里塔尼亚人和11区人的混血儿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.10,0:14:29.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放弃红月 选择斯坦菲尔德这名字的话 就可以很好的生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:32.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是有这种想法的话 想成为Knight of Rounds也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.24,0:14:33.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:37.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是想问你有没有回来这边的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.77,0:14:40.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布兰德利卿 请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.83,0:14:44.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被打成这样 反正是要沉的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.50,0:14:48.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就让卢西亚诺来有效利用一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.41,0:14:50.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一口气解决
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.85,0:14:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然用同伴的舰艇来做武器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.77,0:14:55.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持炮击 全速后退
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.51,0:14:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.15,0:15:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.10,0:15:04.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有两下子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.18,0:15:07.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 在这个位置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.98,0:15:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 挺身吃我一剑衔接随后的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.63,0:15:19.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星刻此人 被称为麒麟儿看来并非浪得虚名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.07,0:15:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星刻总司令好像负伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.37,0:15:24.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大龙胆 后退
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.38,0:15:27.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作战指挥转移给参谋长周香凛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.08,0:15:29.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没到时候吗 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:34.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO的真面目居然真的是学生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.32,0:15:37.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉尔弗德
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.07,0:15:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.72,0:15:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇族杀手ZERO的真面目居然是我的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:45.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是何等的悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:48.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇兄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.37,0:15:52.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 鲁路修 皇帝陛下那边由我来周旋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.73,0:15:58.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 责罚是不可避免 你的性命我或许还能保住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:16:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想怜悯我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.36,0:16:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:07.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 全部是修奈泽尔殿下的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.24,0:16:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是跟着你就能找到ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.56,0:16:16.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下已经察觉到了 你和ZERO不寻常的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.76,0:16:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修 就算是现在我也想扮演你哥哥的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.60,0:16:27.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会害你 能信任我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.81,0:16:29.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信任你?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.24,0:16:31.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 信任你的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.11,0:16:36.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常遗憾 皇兄 我已经不再相信任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:38.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我的友情被出卖了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:42.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉尔弗德卿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.63,0:16:45.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么人 你不是Orange
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 我只是想拜托你点事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.44,0:16:56.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了 要我做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.28,0:16:59.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 很简单的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:07.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当我摆出这个姿势 那一刻你就把我当作科奈莉娅 然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.47,0:17:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科奈莉娅皇女殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.37,0:17:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的骑士吉尔弗德 救我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.73,0:17:16.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes Your Highness
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:19.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亏你注意到了 吉尔弗德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.65,0:17:21.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉尔弗德卿 你这是干什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.78,0:17:25.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们才是 居然逮捕皇女 发疯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.51,0:17:28.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连吉尔弗德卿也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.72,0:17:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然只有相信了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.54,0:17:33.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇女殿下 暂且先离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.71,0:17:34.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.05,0:17:38.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了 我最初也是最后的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.71,0:17:40.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.86,0:17:46.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直无法相信 吉尔弗德卿居然会叛变
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.47,0:17:47.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.93,0:17:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里待机
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.62,0:17:52.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 修奈泽尔殿下的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.89,0:17:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说ZERO出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.16,0:17:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也没被通知
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.52,0:18:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像得知什么非常糟糕的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.63,0:18:02.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想确认一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.92,0:18:05.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有没有对尤菲使用GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.71,0:18:11.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你的话 应该清楚吉尔弗德卿叛变的理由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.67,0:18:15.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及你曾经在神根岛采取的行动的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.70,0:18:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是应该追击ZERO吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.89,0:18:22.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们缺少非常重要的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.54,0:18:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所知道的情报…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.17,0:18:29.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wired-C 确认反应
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.08,0:18:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,取得同步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.13,0:18:33.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ragnarok Backup 进行复位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.73,0:18:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉尔弗德 就这样前往东京租界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.93,0:18:43.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes Your Highness
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.97,0:18:47.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枢木朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.95,0:18:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.74,0:18:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日本人?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.93,0:18:52.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名誉布里塔尼亚人?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.63,0:18:54.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Knight of Seven
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.21,0:18:57.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是枢木玄武首相的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.96,0:18:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修的朋友?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.84,0:19:01.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤菲米娅的骑士?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.68,0:19:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不愿意说的话 我们就只有投身不公平的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.64,0:19:16.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想让这悲哀的连锁持续到何时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.15,0:19:18.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.32,0:19:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,租界结构的修改已经完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.27,0:19:23.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会像以前那样让ZERO破坏这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.54,0:19:25.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捕捉到了 是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.52,0:19:26.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了吗 蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.99,0:19:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备狙击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.65,0:19:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把Vincent打下来也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.76,0:19:37.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们以为我在租界就只是当个学生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.39,0:19:40.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东京租界 现在就让你停止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.73,0:19:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.28,0:19:49.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.84,0:19:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Energy Filler…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gefion Disturber吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.59,0:19:55.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 关于这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.77,0:20:01.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电视机前的各位观众 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.19,0:20:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,播放室的电源好像断了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.51,0:20:07.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 条件就绪了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.90,0:20:08.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤堂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.61,0:20:10.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.09,0:20:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七号作战开始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.37,0:20:12.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斑鸠浮上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.81,0:20:14.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斑鸠浮上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.35,0:20:16.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰队各战斗部队 随时准备浮上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.86,0:20:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扇 现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.59,0:20:19.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.31,0:20:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本舰队就这样穿过东京湾 突入东京租界 和ZERO会合
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.38,0:20:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各员 战斗配置
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.77,0:20:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.32,0:20:33.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.27,0:20:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夺回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.64,0:20:38.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的忠义 为了鲁路修殿下和娜娜莉殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.00,0:20:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 黑骑士团突入东京湾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.60,0:20:47.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦尔德施泰因卿 派我和直属的Grausam Valkyrie队去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.48,0:20:49.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去东京租界吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.86,0:20:52.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么想建功吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.03,0:20:55.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我只是想破坏而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.84,0:20:57.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗洛 你那如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.69,0:20:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 作战已经开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.33,0:21:02.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就去迎接娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.54,0:21:04.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 拜托了 罗洛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.49,0:21:09.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 我错了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.39,0:21:12.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友情什么的是靠不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.35,0:21:14.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静 无情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.70,0:21:19.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不将自我化为完全体 就不能把娜娜莉夺回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.39,0:21:24.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修 从克洛维斯那时我就觉得事有蹊跷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.31,0:21:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 我已经理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.29,0:21:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我理解并接受了 现在所有的牌都在我的手中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.21,0:21:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 一开始就告诉修奈泽尔殿下的话 就不会引发这样的战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.92,0:21:44.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是Knight of Rounds 我不能处罚你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.11,0:21:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心理的罪恶就自己去寻找答案吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.61,0:21:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.69,0:21:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界不会只对你一个人温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.53,0:21:59.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有坐上去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.17,0:22:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐上这装着Freyja的Lancelot
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.58,0:22:04.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用Freyja把鲁路修…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.71,0:23:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你真敢干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.63,0:23:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,欺骗我 践踏我的尊严
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.64,0:23:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,鄙视我的人们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.33,0:23:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定会赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.85,0:23:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我会赢过修奈泽尔 朱雀给你们看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.02,0:23:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你们把我设为目标而行动着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.27,0:23:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 来迎接我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.84,0:24:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,让我来破坏 让我给你们看看绝望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.25,0:24:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我再去迎接娜娜莉 解救卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.56,0:24:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,最后笑的会是我
